      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sorted E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54 straight-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system. This example has had the rear subframe reinforced and the rod bearings addressed, ensuring the structural integrity of the chassis during high-G cornering. The 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile engagement, sending power through a GKN-sourced limited-slip differential. The suspension maintains its factory-tuned damping characteristics, providing the precise turn-in and communicative feedback synonymous with this platform. While the aesthetic reflects honest road use, the powertrain exhibits excellent compression and linear power delivery up to the 8,000 RPM redline.",
